snippet.title: Super fun and humorous ANIMAL videos #7 - Funny animal compilation - Watch & laugh!
snippet.description:
Animals are simply the best, they make us happy and laugh! Just look at all these cats, kittens, puppies, dogs, monkeys, goats, bears, horses,..  how they behave, make funny sounds, sleep and snore, play, fail,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
